lead_paragraph: Mikayla Pivec had seven of her 17 points in the fourth quarter when Oregon State pulled away and the Beavers beat previously unbeaten Oklahoma State 73-54 in the Play 4 Kay Shootout championship game on Wednesday night.

headline.print_headline: Oregon State Beats Oklahoma State in Play 4 Kay Title Game
